    "title": "Entry-Level Fleet Manager at Myntra Logistics Capital India",
    "description": "Grow your career with Myntra Logistics Capital India! We are hiring a Fleet Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Myntra Logistics Capital India:\nMyntra Logistics Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Myntra Logistics Capital India!",
